definitions.definition: Any member of the family Procyonidae , a New World family of the order Carnivora , including the raccoons , coatis , kinkajous , olingos , ringtails and cacomistles .

main_definition: ( zoology ) Any member of the family Procyonidae , a New World family of the order Carnivora , including the raccoons , coatis , kinkajous , olingos , ringtails and cacomistles .
